<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>오늘의 한국어 3문장</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --blue: #1151d3;
      --blue-dark: #0a3ca9;
      --yellow: #ffcc29;
      --paper: #f7f7f8;
      --card: #ececef;
      --ink: #1549bf;
      --text: #1b2b52;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --line: #0d47c8;
      --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(17, 81, 211, 0.18);
      --radius-xl: 34px;
      --radius-lg: 24px;
      --radius-pill: 999px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", "Apple SD Gothic Neo", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: var(--blue);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .frame {
      max-width: 980px;
      margin: 28px auto;
      background: var(--white);
      border: 6px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 34px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .inner {
      padding: 42px 38px 28px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .badge-top {
      width: 72px;
      height: 64px;
      margin: 0 auto 18px;
      background: var(--blue);
      color: var(--yellow);
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 28px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 10px;
      position: relative;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(17, 81, 211, 0.25);
    }

    .badge-top::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -14px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 0;
      height: 0;
      border-left: 10px solid transparent;
      border-right: 10px solid transparent;
      border-top: 16px solid var(--blue);
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 28px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 70px);
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .content-area {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 250px;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: end;
    }

    .cards {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .card-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 84px 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .num {
      width: 76px;
      height: 76px;
      background: var(--blue);
      color: var(--white);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 900;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(17, 81, 211, 0.18);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 22px 28px;
      min-height: 150px;
    }

    .card h2 {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      color: var(--yellow);
      font-size: clamp(26px, 3vw, 42px);
      line-height: 1.05;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      text-shadow:
        -2px -2px 0 var(--blue),
         2px -2px 0 var(--blue),
        -2px  2px 0 var(--blue),
         2px  2px 0 var(--blue);
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-size: clamp(17px, 2vw, 21px);
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .hl {
      color: var(--yellow);
      text-shadow:
        -1px -1px 0 var(--blue),
         1px -1px 0 var(--blue),
        -1px  1px 0 var(--blue),
         1px  1px 0 var(--blue);
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .illust {
      align-self: end;
      min-height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      justify-content: center;
      padding-right: 6px;
    }

    .character {
      width: 236px;
      height: 432px;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 12px 22px rgba(17, 81, 211, 0.12));
    }

    .footer {
      background: var(--blue);
      color: var(--white);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .footer strong {
      font-size: 20px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .content-area {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .illust {
        display: none;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .frame {
        margin: 0;
        border-radius: 0;
        border-left: none;
        border-right: none;
      }
      .inner {
        padding: 28px 18px 24px;
      }
      .card-row {
        grid-template-columns: 62px 1fr;
        gap: 12px;
        align-items: start;
      }
      .num {
        width: 58px;
        height: 58px;
        font-size: 22px;
      }
      .card {
        padding: 18px 18px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="frame">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="badge-top">3</div>
      <h1>읽기 좋은 한국어 카드학습</h1>

      <section class="content-area">
        <div class="cards">
          <div class="card-row">
            <div class="num">01</div>
            <article class="card">
              <h2>오늘 날씨가 정말 좋네요</h2>
              <p>
                <span class="hl">“오늘 날씨가 정말 좋네요.”</span> 입니다.<br/>
                처음 대화를 시작할 때 부담 없이 꺼낼 수 있는 자연스러운 문장입니다.
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>

          <div class="card-row">
            <div class="num">02</div>
            <article class="card">
              <h2>뭐 하고 지내요?</h2>
              <p>
                <span class="hl">“요즘 뭐 하고 지내요?”</span> 는 오랜만에 만난 사람에게 근황을 물을 때 자주 씁니다.<br/>
                친한 친구, 동료, 선배에게 모두 무난하게 사용할 수 있습니다.
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>

          <div class="card-row">
            <div class="num">03</div>
            <article class="card">
              <h2>커피 마실래요?</h2>
              <p>
                <span class="hl">“시간 되시면 같이 커피 마실래요?”</span> 처럼 제안형 문장을 붙이면,<br/>
                짧은 대화를 실제 약속이나 관계 형성으로 자연스럽게 이어갈 수 있습니다.
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="illust" aria-hidden="true">
          <div style="width:236px;height:432px;display:flex;align-items:end;justify-content:center;">
            <div style="width:100%;height:392px;border:4px solid #0d47c8;border-radius:28px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f5f8ff 0%,#eef2fb 100%);padding:18px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between;box-shadow:0 14px 30px rgba(17,81,211,.10);">
              <div>
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.08em;color:#0d47c8;margin-bottom:10px;">DAILY KOREAN</div>
                <div style="font-size:28px;font-weight:900;line-height:1.05;color:#1151d3;letter-spacing:-.04em;margin-bottom:14px;">3 SENTENCES</div>
                <div style="display:grid;gap:10px;">
                  <div style="height:56px;border-radius:18px;background:#1151d3;"></div>
                  <div style="height:56px;border-radius:18px;background:#ffcc29;"></div>
                  <div style="height:56px;border-radius:18px;background:#dce7ff;border:2px solid #0d47c8;"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div style="background:#fff;border:2px solid #0d47c8;border-radius:24px;padding:16px;">
                <div style="height:12px;background:#dce7ff;border-radius:999px;margin-bottom:10px;"></div>
                <div style="height:12px;background:#dce7ff;border-radius:999px;width:82%;margin-bottom:10px;"></div>
                <div style="height:12px;background:#ffec9a;border-radius:999px;width:60%;margin-bottom:18px;"></div>
                <div style="display:flex;align-items:end;gap:8px;height:92px;">
                  <div style="flex:1;background:#1151d3;height:52%;border-radius:14px 14px 8px 8px;"></div>
                  <div style="flex:1;background:#0a3ca9;height:88%;border-radius:14px 14px 8px 8px;"></div>
                  <div style="flex:1;background:#ffcc29;height:65%;border-radius:14px 14px 8px 8px;"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </section>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div><strong>Korean Daily Study</strong></div>
      <div>하루 3문장으로 한국어를 공부하세요</div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
